All Classes

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AllOrders
    This class contains all the orders placed in list format and can be removed and added if needed.
    Cake
    This class is used to represent a cake donut with three potential flavors as selected by the GUI.
    Coffee
    This class is used to represent a coffee with different sizes as selected by the GUI.
    CoffeeView
    This class is the main method for tutition manager, which sets up the GUI and runs it.
    CoffeeViewController
    This class is the controller for the coffee view and manages the responses to any GUI interactions for the coffee view stage.
    Donut
    This class is used to represent a donut where the flavors are decided based on what type of donut is selected.
    DonutHole
    This class is used to represent a donut hole with three potential flavors as selected by the GUI.
    DonutView
    This class is the main method for tutition manager, which sets up the GUI and runs it.
    DonutViewController
    This class is the controller for the donut view and manages the responses to any GUI interactions for the donut view stage.
    Main  
    MainView
    This class is the main method for tutition manager, which sets up the GUI and runs it.
    MainViewController
    This class is the controller for the main view where a user can choose to order items, check their bag, and all store orders
    MenuItem
    This abstract class represents a menu item where other classes extend it such as donuts and coffee.
    Order
    This class represents an order with a unique order number, menu items in list format, and a price field which contains the total price for a given order.
    OrderingBasketController
    This class is the controller for the ordering basket and manages all UI interactions for this view.
    OrderingBasketView
    This class is the main method for tutition manager, which sets up the GUI and runs it.
    OrderMenuController
    This class is the controller for the order menu and manages the responses to any GUI interactions for the order stage.
    OrderMenuView
    This class starts the Order Menu View and essentially deals with all of the orders that the cafe obtains.
    Yeast
    This class is used to represent a yeast donut with six potential flavors as selected by the GUI.
